'''Valmikism''' is a religious movement of [[dalit]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/bharat-bandh-today-punjab-suspends-internet-bus-services-5119950/|title=Bharat bandh today: Punjab suspends Internet, CBSE exams postponed|date=2018-04-02|work=The Indian Express|access-date=2018-07-30|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/minister-for-state-vijay-sampla-faces-opposition-from-dalit-organisations-in-hoshiarpur-5135589/|title=Minister for State Vijay Sampla faces opposition from Dalit organisations in Hoshiarpur|date=2018-04-13|work=The Indian Express|access-date=2018-07-30|language=en-US}}</ref> [[Valmiki caste|Valmiki community]] that worships the Lord [[Valmiki]] as their ancestor and god.<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=UaeoDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT150&lpg=PT150&dq=Valmikism+religion&source=bl&ots=bIhLW3Atmg&sig=7gf3Sg8uzqXS2jTt0eUP4zB7TrA&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjCstDu-8bcAhXEv48KHa_tCXU4ChDoATABegQIARAB#v=onepage&q=Valmikism%20religion&f=false|title=Sikh Identity: An Exploration of Groups Among Sikhs|last=Takhar|first=Opinderjit Kaur|date=2016-12-05|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781351900102|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deccanchronicle.com/nation/current-affairs/100118/madhya-pradesh-minister-calls-valmiki-daaku-sparks-furore.html|title=Madhya Pradesh minister calls Valmiki ‘daaku’, sparks furore|date=2018-01-10|work=Deccan Chronicle|access-date=2018-07-30|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=JRfuJFRV_O8C&pg=PA600&lpg=PA600&dq=Valmikism+religion&source=bl&ots=TNqsUiQT1J&sig=6XQVojIfmPHSUxSGNUn_DR-e6os&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjCstDu-8bcAhXEv48KHa_tCXU4ChDoATAFegQIBRAB#v=onepage&q=Valmiki&f=false|title=A History of Indian Literature|last=Winternitz|first=Moriz|date=1996|publisher=Motilal Banarsidass Publ.|isbn=9788120802643|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books/about/The_Legends_of_th