xis the Man of God's Monastery|region:UA_type:landmark}} |- | 7. | | style="background:#f2f2f2;" |'''[[St. Onuphrius's Monastery (Сhubivka Village, Cherkasy Rgn.) | St. Onuphrius's Monastery]]''' | Cherkasy Rgn., Cherkassy Dst., Village Сhubivka |{{coord|49.223609|32.218806|name=St. Onuphrius's Monastery|region:UA_type:landmark}} |- | 8. | | style="background:#f2f2f2" | '''[[Transfiguration Convent (Stebliv Village, Cherkasy Rgn.) | Transfiguration Convent]]''' | Cherkasy Rgn., Korsun-Shevchenkiv Dst., Village Stebliv, 8 Bereznya Str., 9a | {{coord|49.396937|31.102625|name=Transfiguration Convent|region:UA_type:landmark}} |}
