opol Town, Zaporizhzhya Rgn.) | St. Sabbas the Sanctified's Monastery]]''' — [https://monasteries.org.ua/objects/monasteries/89/?lang=en More]|| width="250px" |Zaporizhzhya Rgn., Town Melitopol, Vorovskoho Str., 45 | width="170px" |{{coord|46.833869|35.375455|name=St. Sabbas the Sanctified's Monastery|region:UA_type:landmark}} |- | align="center" style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="20px" | 5. || style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="150px" | || style="background:#f2f2f2;border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="170px" |'''[[Tikhvin Icon of the Mother of God female skete (Plavni Village, Zaporizhzhya Rgn.) | Tikhvin Icon of the Mother of God female skete]]''' — [https://monasteries.org.ua/objects/monasteries/301/?lang=en More]|| width="250px" |Zaporizhzhya Rgn., Vasyliv Dst., Village Plavni, Naberezhna Str., 89 | width="170px" |{{coord|47.562795|35.330503|name=Tikhvin Icon of the Mother of God female skete|region:UA_type:landmark}} |} == [[ File:Coat of Arms of Zhytomyr Oblast.svg|40px]] [[Zhytomyr Oblast | Zhytomyr Region]] (12) == === [[Diocese of Kiev (Moscow Patriarchate) | Kiev Diocese]] (7) === {| class="wikitable" |- | align="center" style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="20px" | 1. || style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="150px" | || style="background:#f2f2f2;border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="170px" | '''[["Assuage My Sorrows" Icon of the Mother of God stauropegial Convent (Horodnytsya Settlement , Zhytomyr Rgn.) | "Assuage My Sorrows" Icon of the Mother of God stauropegial Convent]]''' — [https://monasteries.org.ua/objects/monasteries/245/?lang=en More] || width="250px" |Zhytomyr Rgn., Novohrad-Volynsk Dst., Settlement Horodnytsya, Monastyrskyy Lane, 1 | width="170px" |{{coord|50.805982|27.314999|name="Assuage My Sorrows" Icon of the Mother of God stauropegial Convent|region:UA_type:landmark}} |- | align="center" style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="20px" | 2. || style="border-bottom:1px solid black;" width="150px"